No limit or boundary stop your action and it is up to you to become legendary monster hero of Wild gorilla city rampage games by causing deep wreckage in all scenarios of city rampage games.

Your all four gigantic animals of city rampage games dinosaur games are with matchless powers and knacks in all areas of action. Make the best use of all these and make dinosaur city attack and crazy elephant city rampage a tale of past.
